<% content_for :title do %>Account Verified<% end %>

<p style="margin: 0 0 1em 0;">Hello <%= @user.email %>,</p>

<div style="background-color: #d4edda; border-left: 4px solid #28a745; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
  <p style="margin: 0 0 1em 0;"><strong style="color: #000;">Great news!</strong> Your account has been verified. You can now start sending postcards!</p>
</div>

<p style="margin: 0 0 1em 0;">You can send postcards by emailing <strong style="color: #000;">send@postcardmailer.us</strong> with the following information:</p>

<div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 5px;">
  <p style="margin: 0 0 1em 0;"><strong style="color: #000;">Subject:</strong> [Your postcard message]</p>
  <p style="margin: 0 0 1em 0;"><strong style="color: #000;">Body:</strong></p>
  <p style="font-family: monospace; background-color: #f1f1f1; padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">to: [recipient nickname or full address]</p>
  <p style="font-family: monospace; background-color: #f1f1f1; padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">image: [attach an image or include a URL to an image]</p>
</div>

<p style="margin: 0 0 1em 0;">For example, you could send:</p>

<div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 5px;">
  <p style="margin: 0 0 1em 0;"><strong style="color: #000;">Subject:</strong> Greetings from San Francisco!</p>
  <p style="margin: 0 0 1em 0;"><strong style="color: #000;">Body:</strong></p>
  <p style="font-family: monospace; background-color: #f1f1f1; padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">to: mom</p>
  <p style="margin: 0 0 1em 0;">Having a great time in California. The weather is beautiful and the food is amazing!</p>
  <p style="margin: 0 0 1em 0;"><em style="color: #666;">[Attached image of the Golden Gate Bridge]</em></p>
</div>

<p style="margin: 0 0 1em 0;">If you have any questions, please contact support.</p> 